headline.print_headline: Wiggins Easily Wins Tour of California
headline.main: Wiggins Easily Wins Tour of California

lead_paragraph: Bradley Wiggins cruised to victory in the Tour of California on Sunday as fellow Briton Mark Cavendish won the final stage around Thousand Oaks.
